164
00:12:34,080 --> 00:12:36,040
She's been clinging to me,

165
00:12:36,210 --> 00:12:37,830
never wanting to let go.

166
00:12:38,110 --> 00:12:39,860
Do you think we can

167
00:12:39,880 --> 00:12:41,570
escape successfully like this?

168
00:12:44,840 --> 00:12:48,300
Your people are everywhere in Mingyi Manor.

169
00:12:48,480 --> 00:12:50,260
And we have no weapons.

170
00:12:50,510 --> 00:12:52,640
Do you think we can escape?

171
00:12:54,280 --> 00:12:56,030
Then why are you so nervous?

172
00:12:57,710 --> 00:12:59,850
We let her out.

173
00:12:59,870 --> 00:13:01,390
That makes us a little worried.

174
00:13:03,490 --> 00:13:05,360
You can imagine this courtyard

175
00:13:05,400 --> 00:13:07,140
as that room.

176
00:13:08,050 --> 00:13:11,520
You two and the disciples around

177
00:13:11,550 --> 00:13:13,400
are like the lock of that room,

178
00:13:13,430 --> 00:13:15,000
locking us in the courtyard.

179
00:13:15,350 --> 00:13:16,960
So what's the difference

180
00:13:16,990 --> 00:13:18,310
between staying in that room

181
00:13:18,340 --> 00:13:19,830
and staying here?

182
00:13:22,520 --> 00:13:23,690
That makes sense.

183
00:13:24,090 --> 00:13:25,770
Come on. Sit down.

184
00:13:25,790 --> 00:13:26,680
Let's eat together later.

185
00:13:37,260 --> 00:13:39,260
