223
00:15:49,650 --> 00:15:50,890
Do you really think

224
00:15:50,920 --> 00:15:53,720
Qing Cai is a woman?

225
00:15:53,790 --> 00:15:54,710
What do you mean?

226
00:15:55,310 --> 00:15:56,810
That's a man.

227
00:16:03,730 --> 00:16:08,970
Does Qing Cai... like women?

228
00:16:12,140 --> 00:16:14,480
I'm a man. I only like women.

229
00:16:14,760 --> 00:16:16,190
I only like women too.

230
00:16:16,640 --> 00:16:18,560
Well, then why are you giving me flowers?

231
00:17:01,360 --> 00:17:02,750
Qing Cai, Gan Pu,

232
00:17:02,950 --> 00:17:04,819
I have bad news for you.

233
00:17:05,180 --> 00:17:07,579
Yinniang... died.

234
00:17:12,099 --> 00:17:14,170
We're going to have an all-hands meeting

235
00:17:14,310 --> 00:17:16,640
to discuss how to deal with Gan Pu.

236
00:17:23,619 --> 00:17:24,400
You guys...

237
00:17:25,109 --> 00:17:26,180
You guys...

238
00:17:41,120 --> 00:17:42,270
I'm sure

239
00:17:42,930 --> 00:17:44,470
Yinniang is dead.

240
00:17:45,760 --> 00:17:47,340
Yinniang was highly skilled in martial arts.

241
00:17:47,370 --> 00:17:48,830
How could she die so easily?

242
00:17:49,240 --> 00:17:50,880
Gan Pu's archery is very impressive.

243
00:17:51,700 --> 00:17:53,310
And it was a sneak attack.

244
00:17:54,620 --> 00:17:56,690
Luckily, Yinniang was highly skilled in martial arts.

245
00:17:57,370 --> 00:17:59,880
When the arrow was released, she moved her body to one side

246
00:18:00,110 --> 00:18:01,280
