250
00:18:11,230 --> 00:18:12,720
She still couldn't be saved.

251
00:18:13,000 --> 00:18:15,190
You both have received clear orders.

252
00:18:17,440 --> 00:18:19,860
You don't have your own ideas, do you?

253
00:18:22,820 --> 00:18:23,650
What a pity.

254
00:18:23,870 --> 00:18:25,900
I really consider Qing Cai as my brother.

255
00:18:27,850 --> 00:18:29,610
