273
00:19:19,270 --> 00:19:20,430
Is it that serious?

274
00:19:20,760 --> 00:19:22,360
I'm a little scared.

275
00:19:23,130 --> 00:19:25,900
I'm sorry for dragging you guys into this.

276
00:19:28,230 --> 00:19:29,570
But now,

277
00:19:30,210 --> 00:19:31,530
